name: Costumzee
tag_list: costume, outfit, disguise, shopping-site, shopping-comparison, social-shopping
overview:
Costumzee is a community of people sharing costume ideas and photos. Sign up to submit your costume ideas and enter the photo contest.

You’ll find thousands of costumes on our site, organized by “tags”. A tag is a descriptive name that represents a concept or idea. A tag may have zero, one, or many costume ideas in it. If you see something you like, add the tag to your profile. Once a tag is added, you can select a specific product to show in your profile. Even upload your own pictures.

Costumzee.com is a community and a shopping portal. We bring people together, with their own costume ideas, or to discover new ideas. Our “idea engine” gives you a quick and easy way to browse through thousands of costume ideas and products.

Our proprietary software ranks products based a complex algorithm which takes in consideration a high number of popularity, relevancy and traffic data factors.
